      private static java.util.Locale findLocale​(java.lang.String input)
      Gets a supported language from the input.

      input can be either the language code or the name of the language itself. Returns DEFAULT_LOCALE if the language is not supported.

      Parameters:
      input - The desired language.
      Returns:
      The Locale object representing the language.
